+   exact closed-support inflow quantities `J_X`, not by packet-itinerary
+   rhetoric.
+2. The delayed-transfer metric sheet freezes intrinsic clocks, one
+   target-transfer threshold, one spectator-burden threshold, and a
+   non-single-trajectory robustness rule.
+3. Step 2 is well-posed once the branch carries the intrinsic triad-phase
+   ledger, the recursively exact helical-support search class, and the frozen
+   metric sheet together.
